@node "amihunter" "AmiHunter.amirx"

@{b}What is AmiHunter@{ub}


  What is AmiHunter, Well kinda a Cross between Aminetfind.amirx &      
  AmircFetch.amirx.  


  So Realy what is AmiHunter.  AmiHunter lets you search and download   
  from aminet via Amirc & Zed_httpget. Amnetfind.amirx worked great for 
  finding files, but didn't download. Amircfetch.amirx used ftpget to   
  download and required you to type in the full path of file you wanted 
  to download, and had no progress indicator of the file progess.      
  So AmiHunter was born, Which Searches/Gets/Views Readme's of the 
  requested files all in and has a download progress GUI. 

  AmiHunter is EMailware and included in Kuangąą 3.0.

  Email: bosman@erols.com
   
                    http://www.erols.com/bosman/

     @{"Send IBrowse" rxs "if show('P','IBROWSE') then do;address IBROWSE;'GOTOURL http://www.erols.com/bosman/';end"} @{"Send Voyager" rxs "if show('P','VOYAGER') then do;address VOYAGER;'OPENURL http://www.erols.com/bosman/';end"} @{"Send AWEB   " rxs "if show('P','AWEB.1') then do;address AWEB.1;'OPEN http://www.erols.com/bosman/';end"}

@endnode
